316
00:32:19,531 --> 00:32:21,084
You should open a restaurant.

317
00:32:21,084 --> 00:32:22,085
Of course.

318
00:32:22,983 --> 00:32:24,063
That sausage…

319
00:32:25,364 --> 00:32:26,379
I bought it.

320
00:32:28,847 --> 00:32:31,487
