342
00:33:51,582 --> 00:33:53,988
Well, shouldn't we find a way
to protect ourselves from them?

343
00:33:59,682 --> 00:34:01,680
Well, we should find a way
to protect ourselves from them, right?

344
00:34:01,680 --> 00:34:04,120
