354
00:34:30,920 --> 00:34:31,924
I'm sorry.

355
00:34:32,512 --> 00:34:35,371
Jee! Have some manners!

356
00:34:35,371 --> 00:34:36,376
Grandma!

357
00:34:38,444 --> 00:34:40,173
I can have manners.

358
00:34:40,173 --> 00:34:43,280
