400
00:38:17,418 --> 00:38:19,261
Last night, when I went down
to get some stuff,

401
00:38:20,357 --> 00:38:21,658
I saw him with Fah.

402
00:38:33,360 --> 00:38:34,610
See you the day after tomorrow.

