424
00:39:49,920 --> 00:39:51,127
15 reps, 3 sets.

425
00:39:51,127 --> 00:39:52,320
Okay.

426
00:39:52,320 --> 00:39:53,680
Okay. Up.

427
00:39:54,249 --> 00:39:56,449
1, breathe out…

428
00:39:58,331 --> 00:39:59,791
Breathe out, hold it.

429
00:39:59,791 --> 00:40:00,880
Good. Keep focusing.

